updating a (readonly text) custom field with an empty string does not work.
If i send this :
{code}
{
    "fields":
    {
        "customfield_10307":""
    }
}
{code}
or this :
{code}
{
    "update":
    {
        "customfield_10307": [
            { "set": "" }
        ]
    }
}
{code}

I receive a 204 like if everything was alright. 
But the issue is not updated. The value in the text field is still the same.

If i send a string (not empty), the update works.

Am I missing something here ?
Thanks.

